{"name":"Godendag","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-simple-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy staff topped with a spiked iron ball, the godendag combines the reach of a spear with the crushing power of a mace.</p>"},"price":{"value":12,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you score a mighty blow, the next attack against this target gains advantage."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Hand Spear","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/javelin-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A short, balanced spear designed for one-handed use, equally suited for melee combat and throwing.</p>"},"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":40,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you make a second attack on your turn against the same creature, that attack has advantage and you ignore all sources of disadvantage for that attack."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Harpoon","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/trident-silver.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy barbed spear designed to pierce and lodge in flesh, preventing escape. Favored by hunters and fishermen alike.</p>"},"price":{"value":11,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You drag an enemy toward you a number of feet equal to twice your Strength score, and your target suffers disadvantage to Strength saving throws while it is impaled."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Javelin","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/javelin-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A light throwing spear balanced for long-range accuracy. Javelins are a staple of soldiers and hunters across the world.</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":30,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you score a mighty blow, the target suffers a -2 AC penalty. On its turn an enemy can use an action to succeed on a Strength saving throw to pry the javelin free, destroying it in the process."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Lance","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-simple-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A long cavalry weapon designed to be used from horseback, the lance delivers devastating charges and keeps foes at bay.</p>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":12,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can attempt a Shove as a bonus action. While mounted, after you successfully hit a target, you can attempt a shove as part of the attack and gain advantage in the roll. Additionally, you no longer suffer disadvantage to attack rolls when you use this weapon on foot."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Pike","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/halberd-crescent-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>An extremely long polearm used in tight formations, the pike keeps enemies at a distance and can brace against charges.</p>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":8,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":12,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","hvy","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You ignore half cover. Additionally, if you hit with an attack on a target more than 5 ft away, it cannot move closer to you until the end of its next turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Ravenbeak","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-simple-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>An elegantly crafted spear with a hooked blade resembling a raven's beak, designed to disarm foes and riposte swiftly.</p>"},"price":{"value":15,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":30,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","ver","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you hit with an attack, you can move your target 5 ft in a direction of your choice, and it can't move closer to you until the start of your next turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Trident","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/trident-silver.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A three-pronged spear used both on land and at sea, the trident's multiple points are excellent for catching and disarming opponents.</p>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":2,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["ver","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can Deflect attacks against any target in reach. When you wield a trident with two hands, your enemy must succeed on a Strength saving throw or be disarmed when you Deflect."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"War Spear","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-simple-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A versatile combat spear reinforced for the rigors of war, featuring a double-ended design that rewards skilled wielders.</p>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["ver","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you use this weapon one-handed, you can use Double Ended as if you were using it with two hands. In two hands, you deal an extra d4 weapon damage each time you hit with the main melee attack."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Winged Spear","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/spear-simple-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A spear with cross-guards or 'wings' near the blade that prevent over-penetration and allow for deflecting and repositioning opponents.</p>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1.5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":30,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","ver","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Spears","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you hit with an attack, you can move your target 5 ft in a direction of your choice, and it can't move closer to you until the start of your next turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Bladewing","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/boomerang-wood.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A large, heavy bladed disc that returns after being thrown. In skilled hands it can cut through entire formations of enemies.</p>"},"price":{"value":15,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["bludgeoning","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":60,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","hvy","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Once on your turn, using one of your attacks, you can make an attack against all creatures in a 30 foot line, 5 feet wide, before the bladewing returns."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Bolas","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/bolas-leather.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Weighted balls connected by cord, the bolas are thrown to entangle and trip opponents, restraining them in place.</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":30,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When your Entangle attack hits, the target must succeed on the save or become prone and restrained."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Boomerang","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/boomerang-wood.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A curved throwing weapon that returns to the thrower when it misses. Useful for striking multiple targets in a single throw.</p>"},"price":{"value":3,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":40,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Once on your turn, you can choose two targets within 40ft to attack with the same attack."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Chakram","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/shuriken-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A flat circular blade with a sharpened outer edge, the chakram is both a melee weapon and a deadly thrown disc.</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"sp"},"weight":{"value":0.5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":40,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If a creature misses you with an attack, as a reaction you can attack that creature."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Dart","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/dart-poison.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A small, weighted needle that can be thrown with surprising accuracy. Often used to deliver poisons or pin enemies in place.</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"sp"},"weight":{"value":0.05,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":30,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can deal no damage on hit and pin the enemy to an adjacent wall or obstacle causing your enemy to be restrained. The escape DC is your weapon DC."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Kunai","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/knife-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A multi-purpose blade used for throwing, climbing, and close combat. Its ring pommel allows for spinning deflection techniques.</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"sp"},"weight":{"value":0.25,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can use Deflect within your normal range, and for any creature of your choice."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Mambele","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/knife-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A multi-bladed throwing knife with curved secondary blades, the mambele tumbles in flight and can deflect incoming attacks.</p>"},"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":40,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you Deflect any damage from a melee weapon, you can Wound your enemy."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Net","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/net-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A weighted net thrown to entangle opponents. The net itself deals no damage but can incapacitate enemies effectively.</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":0,"denomination":1,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":20,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"The net's AC is equal to your weapon DC. If you have advantage on an Entangle attack, your target has disadvantage on the check made to escape."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Throwing Knife","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/knife-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A balanced blade optimized for throwing, the throwing knife can be used in melee or launched to distract and hobble enemies.</p>"},"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"sp"},"weight":{"value":0.5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":30,"long":90,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can deal only your Strength or Dexterity modifier in damage, but force your target to succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or lose its reaction and suffer disadvantage on its next attack."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Throwing Shot","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/bolas-leather.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy iron ball thrown with tremendous force, the throwing shot staggers and knocks down enemies through sheer impact.</p>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"sp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you score a critical hit or have advantage and both rolls would have hit, your enemy must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or be stunned until the end of its next turn. If you have disadvantage but one dice would have hit, deal your Strength modifier in damage, though this still counts as a miss."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Throwing Star","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/shuriken-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A small multi-pointed metal disc that can be thrown with deadly accuracy. Easy to conceal and carry in quantity.</p>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"sp"},"weight":{"value":0.05,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Throwing Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As an action, you can make a single attack against all targets of your choice within 20 ft of you. You must have enough throwing stars to attack each target."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Kusarigama","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A sickle attached to a weighted chain, the kusarigama can entangle and trip opponents before striking with the blade.</p>"},"price":{"value":30,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","two","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Whips","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you hit with a main attack and Double Ended attack on the same target on the same turn, you can move your target 5 ft in a direction of your choosing."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Meteor Hammer","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A weighted ball on a long flexible chain, the meteor hammer can be used to entangle, trip, or lunge at distant foes.</p>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","two","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Whips","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As a reaction you can enter a readied stance. Until the start of your next turn, you can make an attack against any creature that enters your reach, and doing so does not use your reaction."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Scorpion Whip","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A flexible whip tipped with sharp spines like a scorpion's tail, capable of entangling and puncturing opponents at reach.</p>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Whips","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you choose a different target than your previous attack, the attack roll gains +2."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Scourge","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A multi-tailed whip with weighted or barbed ends, the scourge deals terrible lacerating wounds and excels at disarming foes.</p>"},"price":{"value":3,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Whips","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"This weapon adds two extra damage dice when it scores a critical hit. When an enemy is affected by the Wound property, it takes two damage dice."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Spiked Chain","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/misc/chain-spiked-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A length of chain with sharpened spikes, the spiked chain can disarm, entangle, and build momentum with each successive strike.</p>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Whips","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you miss, add another damage die to the next attack that hits. At the end of your turn, any extra built up damage dice are lost."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"War Poi","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Weighted balls on chains that are lit aflame, the war poi combine the reach and entangling properties of flexible weapons with burning fire damage.</p>"},"price":{"value":15,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning","fire"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","two","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Whips","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you use a property attack, you always deal the fire damage listed."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Whip","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A long leather lash with an extended reach of 15 feet, the whip excels at disarming, entangling, and tripping opponents from a safe distance.</p>"},"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":15,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Whips","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you Disarm, you can place the item anywhere in your reach, or use your reaction to catch it. An item that can be grabbed with the whip can be placed anywhere else in your reach."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Whip Dagger","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A flexible blade that can strike like a whip, the whip dagger can entangle enemies and then exploit that vulnerability to deliver precise strikes.</p>"},"price":{"value":15,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","two","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Whips","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"While an enemy is entangled, you can attack it or any target within 5ft of it. This forgoes the automatic hit granted by the Entangle property, and if this attack hits, it deals weapon damage and your ability modifier."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Whip Sword","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/misc/whip-pointed-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A segmented blade that can be wielded as a rigid sword or released to flow like a whip. Sword Form: a precise one-handed blade. Whip Form: a flexible reach weapon that entangles and trips.</p>"},"price":{"value":150,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","ver"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Whips","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can change between weapon forms freely. Additionally, when you hit with this weapon, you can deal only your Strength modifier in damage and automatically Entangle your enemy by changing to its whip profile."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
